The information retrieval (cs.IR) community may also find this paper relevant because it discusses techniques for optimizing query performance. 

Finally, the software engineering (cs.SE) community may be interested in this paper because it discusses how separating preferences from the main query body can improve the readability and optimization of queries, which is a common concern in software development.
